\n；致重傷者，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或30萬元以下罰金","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e5%8e%9f%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c42%2c20211029%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗原交簡,42,20211029,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗原交簡","JNO":"42","JDATE":"20211029","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}